title: 178: Patrick Mahomes, perfect pairings and favorite players by round
itunes:title: 178: Patrick Mahomes, perfect pairings and favorite players by round
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks give their perfect pairings for the top two picks of every team in the NFC East. They also talk to Texas Tech QB Patrick Mahomes about their draft prep. DJ and Bucky also discuss their favorite players from all 7 rounds and get a classic road story from Jaguars GM David Caldwell’s days as a scout.
